		"ITEM_METEORATTACKONHIGHDAMAGE_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>3%</style> chance on hit to call a meatball strike, dealing <style=cIsDamage>2000%</style> base damage. Every <style=cIsDamage>100%</style> attack damage dealt increases the activation chance by <style=cIsDamage>3%</style> <style=cStack>(+3% per stack)</style> and damage by <style=cIsDamage>150%</style> <style=cStack>(+50% per stack)</style>.",
