		"ITEM_PRIMARYSKILLSHURIKEN_PICKUP": "Activating your <style=cIsUtility>Primary skill</style> also throws a <style=cIsDamage>shuriken</style> that deals <style=cIsDamage>400%</style> <style=cStack>(+100% per stack)</style> base damage. You can hold up to <style=cIsUtility>3</style> <style=cStack>(+1 per stack)</style> <style=cIsDamage>shurikens</style> which all reload over <style=cIsUtility>10</style> seconds.",
		"ITEM_PROTECTIONPOTION_PICKUP": "Gain a <style=cIsHealing>temporary barrier</style> for <style=cIsHealing>100% of your health</style> when falling below <style=cIsHealth>30% health</style>.",
